com.camerontec.catalys.util.fast.template

Interface IInstruction

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IDecimalField, IField, IGroup, IInstructions, INamedInstructions, IRuntimeInstruction, ISequence, ITemplate
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ByteVectorCopy, ByteVectorDefault, ByteVectorDelta, ByteVectorNoOp, ByteVectorTail, ConstantInstruction, CopyBase, DecimalCopy, DecimalDefault, DecimalDelta, DecimalField, DecimalIndividualOperators, DecimalNoOp, DefaultBase, DeltaBase, DeltaBytesBase, FastField, FastGroup, FastInstructions, FastNamedInstructions, FastSequence, FastTemplate, IncrementBase, Int32Copy, Int32Default, Int32Increment, Int32NoOp, Int64Copy, Int64Default, Int64Increment, Int64NoOp, IntegerDelta, RuntimeInstruction, StringAsciiCopy, StringAsciiDefault, StringAsciiDelta, StringAsciiNoOp, StringAsciiTail, StringUnicodeDelta, TailBase, TemplateIDInstruction, Uint32Copy, Uint32Default, Uint32Increment, Uint32NoOp, Uint64Copy, Uint64Default, Uint64Increment, Uint64NoOp, UnicodeCopy, UnicodeDefault, UnicodeNoOp, UnicodeTail

    public interface IInstruction
    FAST instruction - this can be a simple typed field (integer, decimal, asciiString, etc), a group, a sequence or a template reference.

    Instructions are the building blocks of FAST templates.
